            "creation_date": 1435600797,
            "body": "<p>Try get an array of Files in directory:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>File[] array = new File(\"C:\\\\Users\\\\dokania\\\\Desktop\\\\Bio\\\\Casp10\\\\fasta\\\\\").listFiles();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>And then go through all files using foreach cycle<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>for(File file:array){\n    //...\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Maybe you'll need to use FileFilter:<br>\n<a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/FileFilter.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/FileFilter.html<\/a><br>\nin method <code>listFiles()<\/code><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 31122477,
            "question_id": 31122351
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/2b29988bfc1b16608bbc9d2e6c1f0e34?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
